item.title: CVE-2024-3475|2024-05-02T06:00:02.938Z -- Unknown -- Sticky Buttons
item.description: The Sticky Buttons WordPress plugin before 3.2.4 does not have CSRF checks in some bulk actions, which could allow attackers to make logged in admins perform unwanted actions, such as deleting buttons via CSRF attacks
